snippet.textDisplay:
In a case if this song is the season finale, 
Then id sum this whole season as a master piece. 
From showing the warmth of Sindh in AAYI AAYI, through midnights thoughts of 2AM, from the extravaganza of celebrations in MAAROON LAA, to showing that languages can not separate loved ones in HARKALY, from taking a pep talk of motivation in CHAL CHALIYE, through the paths of uncertainity to a ray of hope in O YAARA, from the world of joy and happiness in BLOCKBUSTER, to a tragedy of love and misunderstanding in JHOL, from taking a glitchy future past ride in TURRI JANDI, to going world wide in PIYA PIYA CALLING, and summing this up with lets not forget nature in MEHMAAN. COKE STUDIO SEASON 15 has acheived it all. 

HATS OFF TO THE TEAM AND ESPECIALLY TO XULFI PAA JI FOR THIS MAGICAL JOURNEY AND ALSO FOR INTRODUCING NEW ARTISTS TOO.
